========================================================================

9.1 BRAND COLORS — LIGHT ADAPTATION

Color              Dark Mode      Light Mode     Why Different
Background         #0F0A1A        #F8F5FF        Inverted base
Surface            #1D1B20        #F0EAFC        Tinted surfaces
Card               #2B2930        #FFFFFF        Cards need contrast
Text Primary       #F5F0FF        #1A0533        Inverted for readability
